{"prompt": "Develop a site for an automotive repair shop. The design should be trustworthy, with a safety yellow accent.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Reliable Auto Repair</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #f1c40f;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: url('placeholder_car_hero.jpg'); /* Replace with a high-quality image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.7); /* Dark overlay for readability */\n        }\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000000;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px #000000;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #f1c40f;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #f1c40f;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: #e6b800;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            border-color: #e6b800;\n        }\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .service-item, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            border-left: 5px solid #f1c40f;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover, .contact-info:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .service-item p, .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for consistent sizing */\n        }\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            background: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background: #34495e;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .flex-container {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .flex-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 280px; /* Adjust as needed */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Reliable Auto Repair</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content container\">\n            <h2>Your Vehicle's Safety is Our Priority</h2>\n            <p>Expert diagnostics, honest repairs, and reliable service to keep you on the road.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Schedule Service</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"flex-container\">\n            <div class=\"service-item flex-item\">\n                <h3>Engine Repair</h3>\n                <p>From minor tune-ups to major overhauls, we ensure your engine runs smoothly and efficiently.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item flex-item\">\n                <h3>Brake Service</h3>\n                <p>Your safety depends on your brakes. We offer comprehensive brake inspections and repairs.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item flex-item\">\n                <h3>Oil Changes & Fluid Checks</h3>\n                <p>Essential maintenance to prolong your vehicle's life and performance.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item flex-item\">\n                <h3>Tire Rotation & Alignment</h3>\n                <p>Ensuring even tire wear and a comfortable, safe driving experience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"background-color: #e8f0f0;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At Reliable Auto Repair, we are a team of certified mechanics dedicated to providing top-notch automotive services. We believe in transparency, quality workmanship, and building lasting relationships with our customers. Your trust is our greatest asset.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"flex-container\">\n            <div class=\"contact-info flex-item\">\n                <h3>Visit Our Shop</h3>\n                <p>123 Automotive Lane<br>\n                   Mechanicville, CA 90210</p>\n                <h3>Call Us</h3>\n                <p>(555) 123-4567</p>\n                <h3>Hours</h3>\n                <p>Monday - Friday: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM<br>\n                   Saturday: 9:00 AM - 1:00 PM</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-item\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Reliable Auto Repair. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}